Syntax: check

Check is used in any of the post offices around the land to check for
any mail you may have waiting.  You must be in the presence of a postmaster
(in the post office) for this to work.  Most major towns have a post office.

The <h> mailing system is compliments of Rasmussen from the now
defunct CircleMUD and also of the now defunct JediMUD.

See Also: MAIL, RECEIVE
Related Topics: POST OFFICE
